             was indicted for <rs id="t18190915-184-off980" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18190915-184-off980" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190915-184-off980" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18190915-184-cd981" type="crimeDate">10th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190915-184-off980 t18190915-184-cd981"></join>, 49 lbs. of tea, value 15 l., and one bag, value 1 s.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18190915-184-victim1593" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Wilmott
                  <interp inst="t18190915-184-victim1593" type="surname" value="Wilmott"></interp>
